 />\n<br />\n各位醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"大家留心有無帶耳機嘅黑衣人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"呢一刻未必係戴耳機， <br />\n或者咁講，佢哋唔需要帶耳機架。<br />\n依家佢哋只需要睇手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n適當時幾起哄， 挑釁， 煽動就夠<br />\n<br />\n一定有一班前線兄弟忍唔住， 配合警察一齊郁手 。"},{"pid":"f6e03cf2375c587a0d6fe135130a816a0b221bc0","tid":1456094,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3427014aff1674b33afd58d4fb7bb847ce44c750","tid":1456094,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"一係你班賴死唔走既就有入咗嚟就唔出翻去，破釜沉舟要好似佔中咁係無限期佔領機場<br />\n唔係既話唔該你早d翻屋企<br />\n今時今日唔理你和唔和理非，只要睇你唔順眼，即刻揸架水炮車對住機場噴都做得出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"機場內唔會開水砲車。<br />\n<br />\n最驚係有黑警帶頭要衝入禁區。<br />\n有兄弟根佢衝， 一入到去就仆街。"},{"pid":"e518a813196ac3a7c2d58be7b4a1ab8d7fabb5d1","tid":1456094,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45ecdbe28d1673de56d688d9d0f3a12c7b3f57a7","tid":1456094,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2a7055efe3bc08fe06fcd3f1d21722b2827b3503","tid":1456094,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"幫手俾全世界睇"},{"pid":"afc5f28425f8a11b23952278ccd9d4f8867a8c5d","tid":1456094,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1BXbRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1BXbRB.jpg&h=b09f5995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張都係whatsapp群組收到<br />\n東沖基本上塞到爆"},{"pid":"6e44319b32d827b87cd39dd94c17c57109903bbf","tid":1456094,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\